===Etymology 1===
Originated before 900 from {{etyl|enm}} {{term|been|lang=enm}} < {{etyl|ang}} {{term|beon|lang=ang}}, from {{term|beo|lang=ang}} + {{term|-n|lang=ang}}, infinitive suffix. Irregular forms inherited from the {{etyl|ang}} compound verb {{term|beon-wesan|bēon-wesan|lang=ang}}.

